
Tumse hi pyar karna hai
tumse hi dil lagana hai
tumhare pyar ka yeh dil diwana tha
diwana hai
tumse hi...
ashiqui kehti hai, mere yaar
ishq to hota hai ek baar
jaan hans hans ke dete hum
kabhi jo karte hain, ikarar
jamane bhar ko janeman, yeh afsara sunana hai
tumhare pyar ka yeh dil, diwana tha diwana hai
tumse hi...
tumhi ko maannaa hai dildar,
tumhi se hongi aankhein char
tumhein palkon pe rakheinge,
kareinge hum har lamha deedaar
bada mushkil, mohabbat mein,
tumhe to bhool pana hai
tumhare pyar ka yeh dil,
deewaanaa tha, deewanaa hai.
tumse hi pyar....